# UI Components (`components/membros/`)

## Client-Only Imports
These components are `"use client"`. They may import from:
- `lib/mapeamento/trajetoria.ts` — trajectory steps, categories, totals, `computeTrajectoryInsights`
- `lib/mapeamento/constants.ts` — `MEMBER_FORM_FIELDS`, `CELULA_FORM_FIELDS`
- `lib/mapeamento/types.ts` — `CelulaOption`, `SetorOption`, `MemberListItem`, `MemberFormValues`, `SaveMemberState`, `SaveCelulaState`, `TrajectoryInsights`, etc.
- `lib/mapeamento/routes.ts` — URL builders
- `lib/mapeamento/formatting.ts` — `formatPhone`, `formatBirthDate`, `formatCreatedAt`

Never import from `celulas.ts`, `membros.ts`, `setores.ts`, `rotas.ts`, or `lib/supabase/*`.

## Member Form Contract
- `MemberForm` uses `useActionState` with a server action passed as prop.
- All form `name` attributes use `MEMBER_FORM_FIELDS` constants.
- Trajectory selections are React-controlled state. Selected values are submitted via hidden `<input>` elements with `name={MEMBER_FORM_FIELDS.passosConcluidos}` — one per selected step. Server reads them with `formData.getAll(...)`.
- `codigo_acesso` and `celula_id` are also submitted as hidden inputs.
- Do not convert this to uncontrolled checkboxes without also updating `getSelectedPassos` in `lib/mapeamento/membros.ts`.

## Cell Form Contract
- `CelulaForm` uses `useActionState` with `saveSetorCelulaAction`.
- All form `name` attributes use `CELULA_FORM_FIELDS` constants.
- `setor_codigo_acesso` is submitted as a hidden input.

## Insights Panel
- `InsightsPanel` is a reusable client component that accepts `members` and optional `celulas`/`totalCelulas` props.
- It uses `computeTrajectoryInsights` from `trajetoria.ts` — never inline trajectory math.
- When `celulas` prop is provided (setor context), it renders a per-cell trajectory ranking section.
- When `celulas` is not provided (celula context), only general insights are shown.

## Component Structure
- `MemberForm` composes: `CelulaSelector`, `MemberPersonalFields`, `MemberTrajectoryFields`, `SubmitButton`.
- `MemberList` composes: `MemberSelfRegisterShare`, `InsightsPanel`, `MemberTrajectorySheet`.
- `CelulaList` renders cell cards with links to `/lider/[codigo]` and a "Cadastrar celula" button.
- `InsightsPanel` renders: `StatCard` grid, category `ProgressBar` list, and optional `CelulaRankingList`.
- Keep each subcomponent focused on its section. Shared state (form values, errors) is passed as props.

## Key Components
| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `member-list.tsx` | Member listing with trajectory progress bars and insights |
| `celula-list.tsx` | Cell listing for sector view with "Cadastrar celula" button |
| `celula-form.tsx` | Cell creation form (nome, lideres, dia_semana, horario, codigo_acesso) |
| `insights-panel.tsx` | Trajectory insights with stat cards, category progress, and per-cell ranking |
| `setor-context.tsx` | Sector context card for sector header |
| `celula-context.tsx` | Cell context card (`CelulaContextCard`, `CelulaAvatar`) |
| `back-button.tsx` | History-based back navigation in headers |
| `access-code-gate.tsx` | Unified access code form with celula/setor toggle |

## Mobile-First & Accessibility
- Touch targets: minimum 44x44px.
- Use accessible contrast ratios.
- Prefer large, clear labels over icon-only controls.
- Test visual hierarchy on narrow viewports first.
